{"tid":1335632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認識中環，正式啟動。","createTime":"2019-07-20T15:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T16:06:34.000Z","uid":36775,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b9512e7d66874c70553456a4c5f00a5f350ee100","tid":1335632,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:07:54.000Z","msg":"灣仔/金鐘地勢分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1334006/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1334006/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為一個香港人，點可以唔識香港中心商業區嘅地勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6z9eTwP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6z9eTwP.jpg&h=5f19ec7f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n外資=<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">綠色</span></strong><br />\n港資=<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span></strong><br />\n中資=<strong>黑色</strong><br />\n天橋系統=<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">紫色</span></strong><br />\n教堂/領事館=<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n成個中環由多條天橋連接各商業大廈，東至滙豐銀行、西至接近上環 (由交易廣場向西行)，基本上可以通往中環大部份地標同大型商場，例如天橋系統可達香港站 (IFC)，交易廣場、怡和大廈、置地商場s等等。<br />\n<br />\n而中環最主要大型商場係置地建築群同IFC。置地建築群包括遮打大廈、置地商場(中庭)、太子大廈同埋歷山大廈<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>，商場之間有行人天橋連接(就如上述所提及)，就好似PP，商場內有大量名店</strong></span>。要注意嘅係，歷山大廈內有地鐵站入口，所以呢幾個商場有可能似新城市商場，地契有可能包括二十四小時通道。IFC比置地商場s大，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">格局有啲似新城市</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，下面係香港站。<br />\n<br />\n除咗置地商場s同ifc係闊同多名店，由環球廣場開始，往上環方向的商場係比較細同up dup，而且無天橋連接，入咗去好大機會係堀頭路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n地鐵出口 L (中國建設銀行大廈)同 H(歷山大廈)設於大廈或商場內，有可能會閂。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家參觀中環覺得口渴同肚餓想買野食，可以去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6MtdOW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6MtdOW.png&h=7ac2a632&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n行到上環就傻豬豬，又要上山又遠。<br />\n<br />\n以置地廣場為中心<br />\n東行<br />\n-有教堂同美國領事館，往金鐘同香港公園<br />\n<br />\n南行<br />\n- 蘭桂坊 (老細=盛智文)，見盛老闆今日出席撐警集會，作為愛國愛港連登仔，有機會就去支持下。<br />\n<br />\n西行<br />\n-由環球廣場向西行，大約十幾分鐘就可以到上環(其實好近)，途中並無係無大型商場。而商場主要係港資細商場。<br />\n<br />\n北行<br />\n-可由天橋系統直達IFC同交易廣場，但只係得天橋，一旦被封就無得行，容易被block (要由皇后像廣場随道或恒生銀行總部隔離天橋過干諾道中)。但由於IFC有地鐵出口，估計IFC正常情況下至少開到東涌線收車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS: 1. 地鐵出口 L (中國建設銀行大廈)同 H(歷山大廈)設於大廈或商場內，有可能會閂。<br />\n       2. HSBC同渣打九成入唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 建議大懵連登仔一早買定回程車飛，費事八達通啫凸唔夠錢返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c9d3c5990f99a6415b3306d8a5bcaf0b300c3d","tid":1335632,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保障同行手足<br />\n向偽警說不！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【7.21有人冒警】和理非對偽警說不！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335553</a>"},{"pid":"32c3ee548f52a88c2fb4c1074f63b482d34bbd70","tid":1335632,"uid":36775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4b2b347c83a9c1eed38010db33adad9094ea30","tid":1335632,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e5eb07005471eeec729bda151233e70f7dacf1","tid":1335632,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e098cd8b0fe717ff745d81aa69c4f69a5c58009","tid":1335632,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26915f9e60ab2ed526396e3f6994f3f21bda3206","tid":1335632,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64987f5c3dc105effda8b8ed9cddf1846e85068d","tid":1335632,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c87ab0059bbfa6b349c73865562df0995c9686","tid":1335632,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"狗打咬爛玻璃實比外資屌撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f128708d0a58487aa39196f845516aeebe8fe9b","tid":1335632,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qRdp4C.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qRdp4C.gif&h=9e72019f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7801f5940edd7efb04f7b3c73ca606ffe2b173d2","tid":1335632,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818ab8c68fe7c4f6818ac2ae38808f1bcb06f3e2","tid":1335632,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:12:45.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea41e396b85ffbc24e9b32fe09b58638e84559a","tid":1335632,"uid":36775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"有幾點抗爭者愈安全<br />\n1. 有名店的大型商場<br />\n2. 外資商場<br />\n3. 多外國人聚集<br />\n4. 多街坊/普通市民<br />\n<br />\n4個字 投鼠忌器"},{"pid":"c93d83cd42345aadef99e148028536f3a8a40d55","tid":1335632,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"香港公園 公園(戶外設施) 每日上午6時至晚上11時<br />\n不過想問香港公園安全嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05046b6c7fbbe256e24003243a13b82233b53a8c","tid":1335632,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c8ad32d0c88df399463e281260e10538c0bcec52","tid":1335632,"uid":191701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:40:16.000Z","msg":"防暴 雜差 O 記入IFC 打人  放催淚彈 精彩"},{"pid":"4516bd81929809eb1e5260994ecb682b5abe9bea","tid":1335632,"uid":260180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"721"}]}